"""
Selenium is a powerful tool for controlling a web browser through the program.
It is functional for all browsers, works on all major OS and its scripts are written in various
languages i.e Python, Java, C#, etc, we will be working with Python.
"""

"""
Web Drivers :
    Selenium requires a web driver to interface with the chosen browser.
    Web drivers is a package to interact with a web browser.
    It interacts with the web browser or a remote web server through a wire protocol which is common to all.
    You can check out and install the web drivers of your browser choice.

Chrome:    https://sites.google.com/a/chromium.org/chromedriver/downloads
Firefox: https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases
Safari:    https://webkit.org/blog/6900/webdriver-support-in-safari-10/
"""

** This is deprecated
## Download chrome driver from the below location, download the same version as your browser
https://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads

